January is said to be "divorce month."  Divorce lawyers report that more folks file for a divorce in January than in any other month. So just in time, <em><a href="http://www.superlawyers.com/illinois">Super Lawyers Magazine</a> </em>has just released  its list of the best or "super" lawyers by region and practice of law. The selection process is actually patented and intended to create a list of top lawyers in various practice areas that both lawyers and consumers can depend on as objective and exceptional. The "Super Divorce Lawyers in Illinois 2015" included  the following lawyers  in the <strong>Top 100 List</strong>:

<strong>Miles N. Beermann at <a href="http://www.beermannlaw.com">Beermann Pritikin Mirabelli Swerdlove</a>, Chicago</strong>

and

<strong>Leon I. Finkel,  David H. Levy, and Berry A. Schatz --- ALL at <a href="http://www.bergerschatz.com">BergerSchatz</a>, Chicago!!</strong>  There were only four family law/divorce lawyers on <a href="http://www.superlawyers.com/illinois">The Top 100 List for 2015.</a>

Full disclosure:  Leon Finkel has been my  fabulous divorce lawyer since 2003.[Is is even legal to say that?]  I joke that he and I have been together longer than most marriages!  He is now the managing partner at <a title="BergerSchatz" href="http://www.bergerschatz.com">BergerSchatz</a>, so I also work with <a href="http://www.bergerschatz.com">Peter Sullivan</a>,  another brilliant partner.  I have been fortunate to have good representation. [We will talk about fees at another time.  Good lawyers are not cheap!]

Leon and Peter  have not only done my two trials and two appeals, but have have assisted me in getting my support on time [a constant battle with the X] and advised me in mediation efforts [but mediation generally does not work for the likes of X].

It is curious that one of the chief rivals of <a href="http://www.bergerschatz.com">BergerSchatz,</a> <a href="http://www.sdflaw.com">Schiller DuCanto</a> has no one on the  top 100 list!  My X's attorney is with that firm. From trusted sources, I have heard that they have many fine and talented lawyers.

<strong>More Super Divorce Lawyers 2015</strong>

In addition to the <strong>Top 100 list,</strong> there is a more <a href="http://www.superlawyers.com/illinois">extensive list of best family law/divorce lawyers, </a> consisting of three print pages.  At the least, a potential litigant should see if lawyers you plan to interview are on that list. However, there are some firms on that list that I would not touch in a million years.  I have heard horror stories of cases gone wrong at those firms.  As litigants, we come and go.*  Lawyers and judges remain constant players. So careful selection of your divorce lawyer is a must!

[*except for me:  we are awaiting the Illinois Appellate Court decision from the second trial!  I have been in the system for 12 years.  Please note that this is not my choice to be here as I have tried every which way out by offering a win-win settlement. As the saying goes, when life gives you lemons, make lemonade. ]

